            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Arcuius <lb n="2"/>aram pos<supplied reason="lost">u</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/>it pro vo<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>o <expan><abbr>dom</abbr><ex>ini</ex></expan> A<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/>corougi a <lb n="6"/>vesu <note>sic</note> con<lb break="no" n="7"/>servis d<lb break="no" n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>o ubicu<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied> <note>sic</note> <lb n="9"/>terraru<supplied reason="lost">m</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Arcuius / aram pos[u]/it pro vo[t]/o dom(ino) A[e]/co Rougia/vesucon/servis d/[e]i ubicu[e] / terraru[m]. (C): kein christlich beeinflußter Nachtrag. Wiedergabe des Textes nach Lesung G. Alföldy.</p>
            </div>
